OL,4,CBenefit death reviews 'shrouded in
OL,5,Csecrecy'
OL,6, Cases where a person claiming benefits
OL,7, died or came to serious harm have now
OL,8, prompted 268 internal reviews since
OL,9, 2012, it can be revealed.
OL,11,FThe Department for Work & Pensions
OL,12,Fholds reviews when it is alleged its
OL,13,Factions had a negative impact, or when
OL,14,Fnamed at an inquest.
OL,16,FIt follows a BBC investigation into the
OL,17,Fscale of deaths earlier this year.
OL,19,FThe Labour party is now calling for an
OL,20,F"urgent independent investigation" into
OL,21,Fbenefits assessments.
